commentary: Gabriel to Tamim Iqbal, OUT down the track again, and this time Gabriel bangs it in short, invites Tamim to hit the shoulder-high ball over mid-off. Goes through with the shot, ends up hitting it high rather than far, and he ends up hitting it down the throat of Holder at mid-off. An exchange of words between Gabriel and Tamim as he makes his way off the ground

commentary: Gabriel to Sabbir Rahman, OUT big appeal, given! Back of a length, and it nips in and keeps a touch low, maybe. commentary: Allen to Mosaddek Hossain, SIX runs switch hit for six! Half-tracker on middle, but he goes left-handed right away, and then slogs it over the point boundary for half-a-dozen. How about that?

commentary: Allen to Mosaddek Hossain, SIX runs Hossain the hero! Full, on off, and he comes down the wicket to lift a six over long off! The crowd's ecstatic

commentary: Allen to Mosaddek Hossain, FOUR runs another one! Bangladesh are romping home now. Quicker from Allen, and Mosaddek is halfway down the track, but he sticks his bat out to play a late cut for four. Delicate
